data.description: 4.25% Assumable VA Loan! Stunning home located in Holbrook Farms! Move in ready! Conveniently located near Thanksgiving Point, Silicon Slopes, restaurants, shopping and future parks and new Hospital. Home features open concept kitchen with large center island, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, soft close cabinets, and under cabinet lighting. Private master suite, office/den, three large living spaces including an upstairs bonus room plus large guest bedrooms creates plenty of space for the whole family! Oversized garage that has been extended for extra storage. Fully fenced backyard and landscaped backyard with incredible mountain views!
